Create File Share:
------------------
Login to Storage account "ukabzfs00"
Navigate to "File Shares"
Click New File Share
File Share Name: s7-public
Tier: Cool
Enable Backup : Default (Ensure Enabled)
Review+Create
 
Add SyncGroup to Azure File Sync:
---------------------------------
Navigate "Storage Sync Services" in Azure portal
Open "hybrid-office-core-storage-sync-service"
Click New Sync group 
Sync group Name: ukabzfs00-Public
Click on "Select Storage Account"
Select ukabzfs00
Select newly created Azure Fil Share "s7-public"
Click "Create"
 
